OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F166A1780635857
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy and rather
OL,6,Fgrey, with outbreaks of rain slowly
OL,7,Fmoving north-eastwards through the
OL,8,Fday. Some brighter intervals may
OL,9,Fdevelop later in the evening. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,13,FIncreasingly cloudy and breezy on
OL,14,FSunday, with patchy light rain late.
OL,15,FBand of rain moving east on Monday.
OL,16,FCooler and windy on Tuesday, with
OL,17,Fsunny spells and showers, occasionally
OL,18,Fheavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
